     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xml:lang=\"fr\" lang=\"fr\"><hr/><p><b>French</b></p><hr/><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Narratif généré : CarteDeConcepts FRPregnancyHistoryLMCDAFHIR</b></p><a name=\"FRPregnancyHistoryLMCDAFHIR\"> </a><a name=\"hcFRPregnancyHistoryLMCDAFHIR\"> </a><p>This mapping does not specify any particular context of use.</p><br/><p><b>Groupe 1 </b>Mapping de <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-lm-historique-grossesse</code> to <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-cda-historique-de-la-grossesse</code></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Code source</b></td><td><b>relation</b></td><td><b>Code cible</b></td></tr><tr><td>FRLMHistoriqueGrossesse</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDAHistoriqueDeLaGrossesse</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMHistoriqueGrossesse.identifiant</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDAHistoriqueDeLaGrossesse.id</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMHistoriqueGrossesse.code</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDAHistoriqueDeLaGrossesse.code</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMHistoriqueGrossesse.statut</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDAHistoriqueDeLaGrossesse.statusCode</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMHistoriqueGrossesse.periodeGrossesse</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDAHistoriqueDeLaGrossesse.effectiveTime</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMHistoriqueGrossesse.choice[x]</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDAHistoriqueDeLaGrossesse.entryRelationship:frObservationSurLaGrossesse</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMHistoriqueGrossesse.choice[x]</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDAHistoriqueDeLaGrossesse.entryRelationship:frNaissance</td></tr></table><hr/><p><b>Groupe 2 </b>Mapping de <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-cda-historique-de-la-grossesse</code> to <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-pregnancy-history-document</code></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Code source</b></td><td><b>relation</b></td><td><b>Code cible</b></td></tr><tr><td>FRCDAHistoriqueDeLaGrossesse</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRPregnancyHistoryDocument</td></tr><tr><td>FRCDAHistoriqueDeLaGrossesse.id</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRPregnancyHistoryDocument.identifier</td></tr><tr><td>FRCDAHistoriqueDeLaGrossesse.code</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRPregnancyHistoryDocument.code</td></tr><tr><td>FRCDAHistoriqueDeLaGrossesse.effectiveTime</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRPregnancyHistoryDocument.date</td></tr><tr><td>FRCDAHistoriqueDeLaGrossesse.entryRelationship:frObservationSurLaGrossesse</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRPregnancyHistoryDocument.entry.item:FRObservationPregnancyDocument</td></tr><tr